14 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this remarkable and distinguished
15 Georgian be recognized appropriately by dedicating an interchange in his memory.
16 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED AND ENACTED BY THE GENERAL
17 ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA that the interchange of Interstate 20 and State Route 92 in
18 Douglas County is dedicated as the Samuel Micah Moon Memorial Interchange.
19 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Department of Transportation is authorized and
20 directed to erect and maintain appropriate signs dedicating the Samuel Micah Moon
21 Memorial Interchange.
22 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
23 to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the family of Mr.
24 Samuel Micah Moon and to the Department of Transportation.
